                        <condition key="deficient">The front board is missing. &#xD;
The back board is loosely attached to the textblock. &#xD;
The textblock is divided into two parts due to the damaged sewing between quires XVIII and XIX. &#xD;
Fol. 1 is mutilated, fol. 2 is discolored, cockled, its right margin is cut. &#xD;
Fol. 255 is mutilated. &#xD;
Some fols. are cockled, stained with water and with wax. (passages of the text on fols. 43rb and 101rab are hardly legible due to water damage). &#xD;
The spine shows concave distortion.</condition>
